1 - nano website_health_check.sh
2 - Paste the script.
3 - Press Ctrl + O to save.
    Press Enter to confirm the filename.
    Press Ctrl + X to exit Nano.
4 - chmod +x website_health_check.sh
5 - nano urls.txt
    https://example.com
    ctrl +o, enter, ctrl +x 
6 - sudo apt update
    sudo apt install curl mailutils
7 - ./website_health_check.sh (Run the script)
